 la diffusion des connaissances et des techniques dont disposait l'ordre, actif dans toute l'Europe. Parmi les innovations agricoles, on peut compter la rotation triennale, la charrue \u00e0 roue, des proc\u00e9d\u00e9s de greffage, ainsi que la culture de nouvelles sortes de fruits. La transformation des conditions \u00e9conomiques g\u00e9n\u00e9rales au bas Moyen Age entra\u00eena le d\u00e9clin de ce syst\u00e8me d'exploitation."]], "text_links": [[], [{"start": 128, "end": 148, "mention": "r\u00e9serve seigneuriale", "href": "/fr/articles/025974/2011-03-23/", "dhsid": "025974", "wiki_links": [], "wikidata_url": null, "wikipedia_page_title": null}, {"start": 165, "end": 176, "mention": "cisterciens", "href": "/fr/articles/011712/2015-05-19/", "dhsid": "011712", "wiki_links": [], "wikidata_url": null, "wikipedia_page_title": null}, {"start": 11, "end": 32, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q3062125", "wikipedia_page_id": 18659, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3062125", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "syst\u00e8me d'exploitation", "confidence_score": 0.9761, "domains": ["Electrotechnology", "Computer_Science"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}}, {"start": 41, "end": 56, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q286576", "wikipedia_page_id": 106817, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q286576", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "syst\u00e8me d'exploitation", "confidence_score": 0.9761, "domains": ["Electrotechnology", "Computer_Science"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}}, {"start": 128, "end": 148, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q3457107", "wikipedia_page_id": 791190, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3457107", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"r